* Lot 192 in RP 93882 - Former Bar/Bistro on Chevron Island
* Single level commercial building on prominent 420sqm* site;
* Gross Lettable Floor Area of 350sqm*;
* Located 1km* from Surfers Paradise CBD;
* Fit-out includes Bar & Commercial Kitchen
* Permissible Development Potential to max 8 Storey (Subject to Council Approval)
* Opportunity to suit investor or owner occupier
* Exposure to vehicle and pedestrian traffic along Thomas Drive;
* Sale includes Liquor Licence (subject to transfer approval by the Office of Liquor Gaming and Racing).

Expressions of Interest close 4.00pm Thursday 12th September 2013

Contact the exclusive listed agents today for a copy of the full information memorandum or to arrange an inspection.
